  characterName: Cowtana
  frames:
  - characterDialogue: That's a crashed Milkstroyer. And a bunch of Cowvenant grunts.
      Could this be the remains of the Halo ring we destroyed last game?
    responses:
    - How could all these things get here?
  - characterDialogue: I don't know. None of it makes sense. Hopefully the last Point
      of Interest will summarize everything nicely and not leave us with an ambiguous
      jump scare ending!
    responses:
    - Alright then let's go.
